findings.title: L09 - Dead Code Elimination
findings.description: Dead code in Solidity contract makes it difficult to understand and maintain, increasing deployment and interaction costs.

findings.title: L18 - Multiple Pragma Directives
findings.description: Including multiple conflicting pragma directives may produce unexpected errors.

findings.title: L19 - Stable Compiler Version
findings.description: The `^` symbol indicates compatibility with any higher version, and the team should lock the pragma to ensure stability.
